## 1. Product Overview

### What is KnowBase AI?

KnowBase AI is an **enterprise-grade, AI-powered knowledge management platform** that enables organizations to upload documents, automatically index their content using vector embeddings, and then chat with their data using **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)**.

### The Problem It Solves

| Problem | KnowBase AI Solution |
|---|---|
| Employees waste hours searching through PDFs | Upload once, ask questions instantly |
| Important info is buried in 100-page documents | AI extracts and retrieves the exact relevant section |
| Generic AI (ChatGPT) doesn't know your company data | RAG grounds answers in YOUR actual documents |
| Multiple departments need separate knowledge bases | Multi-tenant isolation — each user has their own private data |
| No way to know if AI answers are accurate | RAGAS evaluation pipeline measures retrieval and answer quality |

### Who Is It For?

- **AI startups** building knowledge-base products for their customers
- **Enterprises** managing internal documentation (SOPs, policies, reports)
- **Research teams** querying academic papers and datasets
- **Legal firms** searching through case files and contracts
- **Students/Developers** learning production RAG architecture

### Key Capabilities

```
✅ PDF Upload → Auto-chunking → Vector Embedding → PGVector Storage
✅ Hybrid Search (BM25 Keyword + Vector Semantic + Reciprocal Rank Fusion)
✅ Streaming LLM Responses (Server-Sent Events, token-by-token)
✅ RAG Quality Evaluation (RAGAS: Precision, Recall, Faithfulness, Relevance)
✅ Multi-Tenant Data Isolation (each user sees only their own data)
✅ JWT Authentication (register, login, protected routes)
✅ Dashboard Analytics (document count, chat count, performance metrics)
✅ Dark/Light Theme with Responsive UI
```

