## 2. Complete Tech Stack

### Backend (Python)

| Technology | Version | Purpose | Why This Choice |
|---|---|---|---|
| **FastAPI** | >= 0.100 | REST API framework | Async-native, auto Swagger docs, Pydantic validation |
| **SQLAlchemy 2.0** | >= 2.0 | Async ORM | Industry-standard Python ORM with full async support |
| **asyncpg** | >= 0.28 | PostgreSQL driver | Fastest async PostgreSQL driver for Python |
| **PGVector** | >= 0.2 | Vector similarity search | Native PostgreSQL extension — no separate vector DB needed |
| **Google Gemini API** | latest | LLM + Embeddings | Free tier, high quality, supports streaming |
| **PyPDF2** | >= 3.0 | PDF text extraction | Lightweight, pure Python, no system dependencies |
| **python-jose** | >= 3.3 | JWT token handling | Industry-standard JWT creation and validation |
| **bcrypt** | >= 4.0 | Password hashing | Military-grade, salted password security |
| **Pydantic v2** | >= 2.0 | Data validation | Type-safe request/response schemas |
| **Uvicorn** | >= 0.23 | ASGI web server | Production-ready async server |
| **httpx** | >= 0.27 | Async HTTP client | For Gemini API calls with timeout control |
| **RAGAS** | >= 0.1 | RAG evaluation | Industry-standard RAG quality metrics |
| **LangChain Google GenAI** | >= 1.0 | RAGAS LLM backend | Connects RAGAS to Gemini for evaluation |

### Frontend (TypeScript)

| Technology | Version | Purpose | Why This Choice |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Next.js** | 15.1 | React framework | App Router, SSR, file-based routing |
| **React** | 19.0 | UI library | Component-based reactive rendering |
| **TypeScript** | 5.x | Type-safe JS | Fewer bugs, better IDE support |
| **Tailwind CSS** | 3.4 | Utility-first CSS | Rapid styling, built-in dark mode |
| **Axios** | 1.7 | HTTP client | Request interceptors for JWT, timeout handling |
| **Framer Motion** | 11.x | Animations | Smooth page transitions and micro-animations |
| **Lucide React** | 0.468 | Icon library | Clean, consistent SVG icons |
| **React Markdown** | 10.x | Markdown renderer | Renders LLM responses with formatting |

### Infrastructure

| Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|
| **PostgreSQL** | Primary relational database |
| **PGVector Extension** | Vector similarity search within PostgreSQL |
| **PostgreSQL tsvector** | BM25 full-text keyword search |
| **Railway** | Cloud PostgreSQL hosting |
| **Docker + Compose** | Containerized multi-service deployment |
| **JWT (HS256)** | Stateless authentication tokens |

### Architecture Pattern

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   CLIENT LAYER                       │
│              Next.js 15 + React 19                   │
│         (TypeScript, Tailwind, Framer Motion)        │
└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                      │ HTTP/SSE (Axios + Fetch)
┌─────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────┐
│                    API LAYER                          │
│              FastAPI + Uvicorn                        │
│       (JWT Auth, CORS, Exception Handling)            │
└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                      │
┌─────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────┐
│                 SERVICE LAYER                         │
│   Hybrid Search | LLM Service | Document Processor   │
│   Embedding Service | RAG Service | Eval Service      │
└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                      │
┌─────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────┐
│                  DATA LAYER                           │
│    PostgreSQL + PGVector + tsvector (BM25)            │
│    (Users, Documents, Embeddings, Chats)              │
└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                      │
┌─────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────┐
│               EXTERNAL SERVICES                      │
│   Google Gemini Embedding API (768-dim vectors)       │
│   Google Gemini 2.5 Flash LLM (generation + stream)   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

