## 6. Database Schema

### Entity Relationship Diagram

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USERS {
        UUID id PK "Primary key, auto-generated"
        String email UK "Unique, indexed"
        String password_hash "bcrypt hashed"
        DateTime created_at "Auto-set on creation"
    }

    DOCUMENTS {
        UUID id PK "Primary key, auto-generated"
        UUID user_id FK "Foreign key to users.id"
        String filename "Original PDF filename"
        DateTime created_at "Auto-set on creation"
    }

    EMBEDDINGS {
        UUID id PK "Primary key, auto-generated"
        UUID user_id FK "Foreign key to users.id (indexed)"
        UUID document_id FK "Foreign key to documents.id (CASCADE DELETE)"
        Text chunk_text "The actual text content of this chunk"
        Vector_768 embedding "768-dimensional float vector (PGVector)"
        TSVECTOR search_vector "Auto-populated by trigger for BM25 search"
    }

    CHATS {
        UUID id PK "Primary key, auto-generated"
        UUID user_id FK "Foreign key to users.id (indexed)"
        Text query "User's original question"
        Text response "LLM-generated answer"
        DateTime created_at "Auto-set on creation"
    }

    USERS ||--o{ DOCUMENTS : "uploads"
    USERS ||--o{ EMBEDDINGS : "owns"
    USERS ||--o{ CHATS : "creates"
    DOCUMENTS ||--o{ EMBEDDINGS : "contains (CASCADE DELETE)"
```

### Database Indexes

| Table | Index Name | Type | Column | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| users | ix_users_email | B-Tree | email | Fast login lookup |
| documents | ix_documents_user_id | B-Tree | user_id | Filter by user |
| embeddings | ix_embeddings_user_id | B-Tree | user_id | Multi-tenant isolation |
| embeddings | ix_embeddings_document_id | B-Tree | document_id | Join queries |
| embeddings | ix_embeddings_search_vector | **GIN** | search_vector | Fast BM25 keyword search |
| embeddings | (default) | IVFFlat/HNSW | embedding | Fast vector similarity search |

### Database Trigger

```sql
-- Auto-generates tsvector whenever chunk_text is inserted or updated
CREATE TRIGGER trg_update_search_vector
BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE OF chunk_text ON embeddings
FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_search_vector();
```

