## 12. What You Can Build Next

### Tier 1: Quick Wins (1-2 hours each)

| Feature | Description | Stack |
|---|---|---|
| **Chat Export** | Download chat history as PDF/Markdown | jsPDF or react-to-pdf |
| **Password Reset** | Email-based password recovery | FastAPI-Mail + SMTP |
| **File Size Limits** | Enforce max upload size per user | FastAPI middleware |
| **Rate Limiting** | Prevent API abuse | slowapi + Redis |
| **Profile Page** | View/edit email, change password | FastAPI + React form |

### Tier 2: Medium Features (3-8 hours each)

| Feature | Description | Stack |
|---|---|---|
| **Multi-File Support** | DOCX, TXT, CSV upload | python-docx, csv module |
| **Chat Sessions** | Group messages into named conversations | New DB table + API |
| **Admin Dashboard** | View all users, system metrics | Role-based auth + admin API |
| **Semantic Search** | Full-text search across all documents | PGVector + BM25 UI |
| **Notification System** | Toast alerts for upload/errors | React hot-toast |
| **Document Preview** | Show PDF in browser | react-pdf |

### Tier 3: Advanced Features (1-3 days each)

| Feature | Description | Stack |
|---|---|---|
| **Reranking** | Cross-encoder reranking after hybrid search | sentence-transformers |
| **Query Expansion** | Auto-expand queries with synonyms | Gemini query rewriting |
| **Knowledge Graph** | Visualize entity relationships | D3.js + entity extraction |
| **Multi-Language** | Support non-English documents | multilingual embeddings |
| **Webhooks** | Notify external systems on events | FastAPI background tasks |
| **Usage Analytics** | Tokens consumed, queries/day charts | Chart.js + tracking API |

### Tier 4: Production Hardening

| Feature | Description | Stack |
|---|---|---|
| **Alembic Migrations** | Versioned database schema changes | alembic init + migration scripts |
| **CI/CD Pipeline** | Auto-deploy on git push | GitHub Actions + Railway/Vercel |
| **Structured Logging** | Centralized logs with correlation IDs | structlog + Sentry |
| **SSL/HTTPS** | Encrypted connections | Nginx + Let's Encrypt |
| **Horizontal Scaling** | Multiple backend instances | Load balancer + Redis sessions |
| **Monitoring** | Uptime, latency, error rate dashboards | Prometheus + Grafana |

